{"text_id":157707,"tokens":["We"," present"," a"," new"," approach"," to"," derive"," irreducible"," metric"," variations"," of"," the"," action"," terms"," associated"," with"," the"," sixth","-","order"," gravity"," theory","."," Our"," method"," aims"," to"," obtain"," the"," approximated"," stress","-","energy"," tensor"," of"," the"," theory"," by"," using"," the"," metric"," variations","."," ","\n\n","We"," start"," by"," constructing"," the"," most"," general"," polynomial"," action"," of"," sixth","-","order"," gravity"," that"," respects"," the"," field"," equations"," and"," has"," a"," well","-","defined"," variational"," principle","."," We"," then"," consider"," variations"," of"," the"," action"," with"," respect"," to"," the"," metric"," and"," obtain"," a"," set"," of"," equations"," that"," need"," to"," be"," solved"," to"," determine"," the"," irreducible"," components"," of"," the"," metric"," variations","."," We"," use"," a"," decomposition"," of"," the"," metric"," that"," naturally"," emerges"," from"," the"," analysis"," of"," the"," field"," equations"," to"," simplify"," the"," computations","."," ","\n\n","Our"," approach"," differs"," from"," previous"," works"," in"," that"," we"," obtain"," a"," closed","-","form"," expression"," for"," the"," metric"," variations",","," which"," allows"," us"," to"," derive"," the"," approximated"," stress","-","energy"," tensor"," of"," the"," theory"," without"," resorting"," to"," numerical"," simulations","."," This"," result"," represents"," a"," significant"," advancement"," towards"," the"," understanding"," of"," the"," properties"," of"," sixth","-","order"," gravity"," and"," its"," connection"," with"," the"," classical"," theories"," of"," gravitation","."," ","\n\n","Our"," motivation"," for"," this"," work"," is"," to"," shed"," light"," on"," the"," properties"," of"," higher","-","order"," gravity"," and"," to"," provide"," a"," tool"," for"," the"," analysis"," of"," astro","physical"," systems"," that"," are"," subject"," to"," strong"," gravitational"," fields","."," The"," method"," presented"," here"," can"," be"," applied"," to"," study"," a"," variety"," of"," problems"," in"," gravitational"," physics",","," such"," as"," black"," hole"," thermodynamics"," and"," the"," dynamics"," of"," compact"," stars","."],"sub_source":"arxiv","model":"gpt-3.5-turbo","label":1}